cs.DS, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.SC 

This paper is about using the GraphBLAS math library standard to enable the manipulation of sparse weight matrices in deep neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SC (Numerical Analysis).
